title: Sunak rejects calls from Truss to fast-track Taiwan's entry to trading bloc
description: Rishi Sunak has rejected Liz Truss's calls for Taiwan to be fast-tracked into a trans-Pacific trading bloc.

title: Pakistan's former prime minister Imran Khan expects arrest as police have 'surrounded' his house
description: Pakistan's former prime minister Imran Khan says police have "surrounded" his house and his arrest is imminent.

title: Ex-French president Nicolas Sarkozy ordered to wear electronic tag
description: Former French president Nicolas Sarkozy will be forced to wear an electronic tag after losing an appeal against his conviction for corruption.

title: Global temperature set to break key heat threshold for first time in next five years
description: The global temperature is set to exceed 1.5C above pre-industrial levels for the first time in the next five years, the World Meteorological Organisation (WMO) has warned.

title: Russian activist 'poisoned, possibly by nerve agent' while on trip to Europe
description: The head of an international organisation fighting for democracy in Russia says she thinks she was "poisoned, possibly by some nerve agent".

title: 300,000-year-old human footprints discovered
description: Scientists have discovered human footprints thought to be 300,000 years old and the earliest ever found in Germany.

title: Kim Jong Un and daughter inspect North Korean military spy satellite
description: North Korean leader Kim Jong Un and his daughter were pictured examining a military spy satellite which the country is expected to launch soon.

title: Cannes kicks off with huge standing ovation for Johnny Depp and award for Michael Douglas
description: Johnny Depp's first film since his defamation trial got a seven-minute-long standing ovation at Cannes, as the film festival kicked off in France.

title: Three dead and thousands evacuated from their homes after flooding in Italy
description: Three people have died while as many as 5,000 people have been evacuated from their homes in northeast Italy due to flooding.

title: Deadly fire at New Zealand hostel is being treated as suspicious
description: A deadly fire at a hostel in New Zealand is being treated as suspicious.

title: Liz Truss urges Rishi Sunak to describe China as a 'threat' to UK security
description: Former prime minister Liz Truss will call for her successor Rishi Sunak to say China is a "threat" to UK security.
